Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ！ ゲホッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴホッ…
